# TypeScript & React

- Use **functional components** and **hooks**. No class components.
- Prefer **explicit props interfaces** (e.g. `ButtonProps`, `ProductCardProps`).
- Use **'use client'** only when the module uses hooks, browser APIs, or event handlers. Keep server components default where possible.
- Export types from slice index: `export type { X } from './model/types'`.
- Use `cn()` from `@/shared/lib/cn` for conditional class names.
